{"tid":296902,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有冇巴打記得屍姫呢套野？","createTime":"2017-06-25T04:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T12:04:32.000Z","uid":4493,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf7da624820ba9953fafe17a2aa90210d9788cc","tid":296902,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"中學嗰時追漫畫 後來冇追<br />\n早一排先知道2014年完咗 尋日終於追返晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/121828_74519cdb1edf0ae8b9a31e0ebb485366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F121828_74519cdb1edf0ae8b9a31e0ebb485366.jpg&h=1408551b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇情好鬼黑暗 除咗男主角之外根本冇好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有動畫版 Gainax改咗好多 可以完全當係平行時空發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/121713_8904007acf65507bfa5180e6e4bf2daf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F121713_8904007acf65507bfa5180e6e4bf2daf.jpg&h=e9d04a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOP ED 唔錯<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ryx8Vo6xPyk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fryx8Vo6xPyk&d=nXRhX7KgZbohkLgfbT8UvEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e607c86a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ryx8Vo6xPyk</a><br />\n<br />\n呢套令我印象最深就係主角同埋其他好人都好鬼廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多時直接俾二打六打柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d58e88c1b47654c7b603e03130dea4e45dab31c","tid":296902,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:43:37.000Z","msg"